                                <p class="card-text">MVC is a design pattern used to decouple user-interface (view), data (model), and application logic (controller). The use of the ASP.NET framework gives you a powerful, patterns-based way to build dynamic websites using the MVC pattern that enables a clean separation of concerns.</p>
